<br>
What we know today as &quot;Humans&quot; are actually descendents of the original humans created by Mithaniel and Erollisi Marr--the Barbarians of the North.  We no longer required the large, husky frames needed in the rought mountainous terrain, and through our separation, we became smaller, more intelligent.<br>
<br>
This is not to say the Barbarians are stupid.  Far from it.  There are many intelligent Northmen and women on Norrath.  However, without the harsh terrain and climate, we were able to focus less on survival and more on intellectual pursuits.<br>
<br>
Then, Erud and his followers crossed the sea to the west, landing on Odus, and creating a new society focused on the development of the mind.<br>
<br>
All this is a natural development of the human.  You are an Erudite.  You have a great capacity for intelligence.<br>
<br>
But, while you may not be a Human, you still are human. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://webpages.charter.net/thewok/jarasig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
